Description: Materials for a three-day workshop on ecological niche modelling
    (ENM) and species distribution modelling (SDM), using Sambar deer
    (Rusa unicolor) in Thailand as the case study. The workshop covers
    virtual species with 'nicheR', environmental sampling-bias thinning with
    'bean', and temporally-explicit SDMs with 'TemporalModelR'.
